            "title": "深证创指上午收报2217.95点升1.92%",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">    深证创业板指数上午收报2217.95点，升1.92%。</span>\n</div>",
